---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Net Worth Calculator by Age" description="Privacy policy for NetWorth. 100% client-side calculation guarantee with zero data collection.">
	<main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 md:py-20">
		<header class="text-center mb-12 space-y-2">
			<h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 dark:text-white tracking-tight">Privacy Policy</h1>
			<p class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-400">Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { month: 'long', day: 'numeric', year: 'numeric' })}</p>
		</header>

		<div class="p-8 md:p-12 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800/80 bg-white/95 dark:bg-slate-900/60 shadow-xl backdrop-blur-xl text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-300 space-y-6 font-normal leading-relaxed">
			<section>
				<h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">1. 100% Client-Side Calculations</h2>
				<p>Your privacy is paramount. NetWorth executes all age, income, and net worth percentile calculations locally in your Web browser. We do not store, record, or transmit your financial inputs to any server.</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">2. Cookies and Local Storage</h2>
				<p>We do not use tracking cookies to build personal user profiles. Local storage may be utilized solely to remember your preferred theme or currency preferences across browser visits.</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">3. Analytics & Ad Networks</h2>
				<p>We use privacy-preserving analytics to understand aggregate traffic patterns. Non-intrusive advertisements served by trusted partners like Google AdSense may be displayed in accordance with standard web privacy rules.</p>
			</section>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>
